  <class_name>LightingControls</class_name>
  <display_name>lighting_controls</display_name>
  <description>This measure applies lighting controls (daylighting sensors, occupancy sensors) to spaces where they are not already present. </description>
  <modeler_description>This measure loops through space types in the model and applies daylighting controls and occupancy sensors where they are not already present. Daylighting sensors are added via the built-in energy plus daylighting objects, while occupancy sensors are applied via a percent LPD reduction by space type based on ASHRAE 90.1 Appendix Table G3.7.</modeler_description>
